name: Let's watch monkeys at Artis
description: Let's be children again and be fascinated by all the animals you can see at Artis.

name: Let's learn how to cook
description: I cook the same five dishes over and over again... looking for some inspiration. Anybody wants to do a cooking class or just a sharing of easy recipes?

name: Let's put googly eyes accross the city
description: I have a bunch of googly eyes and am looking for other people with too much time on their hands to stick them all accross the city. Know some good places?

name: Let's dress up and go to the opera
description: Every now and then I love classical music. It just puts me in another headspace. Plus I love dressing up. Anybody else?
categories: opera, classical music, dress up, culture

name: Let's rave like a hippie at Ruigoord
description: Ruigoord is a hippie commune close to Amsterdam and they have the best psytrance nights. Any other ravers out there?

name: Let's take tinder pictures
description: I'm too embarassed to ask my friends for this but I do need some pictures for the apps. You too?

name: Let's check out jam sessions
description: I know that Noorderlicht cafe is doing jam session every Sunday, do you know of any other ones?

name: Let's volunteer somewhere
description: At vca.nu you can find so many projects that need volunteers. Want to check out one together?

name: Let's eat at non-commercial restaurants
description: I know of De Peper but I'm sure there are other ones in Amsterdam.

name: Let's go slacklining
description: I have a slackline and know a few good spots. Anybody wants to join? I usually go on Saturdays.

name: Let's start a book club
description: Nerdy, I know, but I love to read and love even more discussing with others what I just read. Currently into classics but open to anything fiction.

name: Let's start a podcast club
description: Like a book club but for podcasts. I'm listenting a lot to Tim Ferris and Ezra Klein. You?

name: Let's get cheap tickets on ticketswap
description: Quite a few bargains on ticketswap usually - want to join for a random concert?
categories: live music, music, festivals, random, yolo

name: Let's learn salsa dancing
description: Can't dance a single step but I always wanted to give it a try. Bachata would also work. Anybody wants to partner up?

name: Let's start a startup
description: I have 100 ideas but never dared to make the first step to do something with them. Maybe there is somebody out there who wants to explore together what it would take to make this dream a reality?

name: Let's take a train to Pairs
description: Paris is so close and yet I never go... Here's the plan: We take the train Sunday morning, get a nice lunch by the Seine, go our own ways for a few hours, get an early dinner and share stories, and then be back in Amsterdam around 10. Who's in?

name: Let's play board games on a rainy day
description: It's Amsterdam - we have more rainy days than any other country it feels like. Who wants to meet at Cafe Brecht on a rainy Saturday afternoon and play some boardgames?
categories: board games, cafe brecht, weekend, rain

name: Let's learn how to play guitar
description: I have a guitar but like 90% of the other people with guitars, I can only play Wonderwall by Oasis. If you're one of these 90% people out there, want to try to get better together?

name: Let's go see some movies
description: I have a cineville card and am always looking for people to go see movies with. Weekday evenings work best for me.

name: Let's play basketball
description: New to the city and looking for a casual team. Ideally something like training once a week.

name: Let's get a hotdog at IKEA
description: I have to go to IKEA this weekend and it's always more fun with company. Maybe somebody else out there in need of a Billy?

name: Let's figure out crypto
description: My mom asked me the other day if she should invest in bitcoin - I feel like I'm a bit late to this. Who wants to sit together and get nerdy about this?

name: Let's do a potluck dinner
description: Everybody prepares a dish and we all get together and eat. Easy, tasty, fun. Who's in?

name: Let's organize a running dinner
description: The concept: Everybody prepares one dish and we move from house to house to taste them all. We start at mine with appetizers. Who wants to join?

name: Let's crash art gallery parties
description: Let's pretend to be rich and crash some art gallery parties. How difficult can it be?

name: Let's be vegan for a week
description: Let's share the recipes, the struggles, and support each other!

name: Let's fix my terrible fashion style
description: I'll buy you lunch and coffees if you take me shopping and help me figure out how to dress better. It'll be fun. I hope.

name: Let's find the best veggi ramen
description: I absolutely LOVE ramen, but finding good vegetarian ramen is a bit of a challenge. Who wants to join me on a tasting mission?

name: Let's read poems in nature
description: I bring a book with poems, you bring some snacks, we contemplate life.

name: Let's contemplate life over a beer
description: Where are we going? Where are we coming from? What do you see as your purpose? What is spirituality for you? Easier with a beer...

name: Let's start a men's group
description: "Hi my name is Joe and I'm a man" - "Hi Joe". What would you expect from a men's group?

name: Let's become spiritual
description: I don't even know where to start but I feel like there's a bit of a void inside of me and in our society when it comes to spirituality. Who wants to explore that void with me?

name: Let's organize a LAN party
description: Old-school but still the best way to play games together. Who's up for some Age of Empires II?

name: Let's go to a wedding as my +1
description: I have an incredibly boring wedding to go to and my friends are all busy. You get lots of free food and drinks and some good people watching, I will be less bored. Win-win.
